w note inside that folder.</li>\n<li style=\" font-size:14pt; color:#333333;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Click <span style=\" font-weight:600;\">✏️</span> to edit the contents of a note.</li>\n<li style=\" font-size:14pt; color:#333333;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Highlight text and click <span style=\" font-weight:600;\">🔲 Copy</span> to turn it into a 1-click copy block!</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:14pt; font-style:italic; color:#555555;\">Start organizing your code and feel the vibe! ⚡️</span></p></body></html>",
